Usage: deleteIoRowFiller [-help] [-cell {name list}] [-from <coord>]
                         [-ioRow <rowName>] [-logic] [-prefix <string>]
                         [-to <coord>]

-help                 # Prints out the command usage
-cell {name list}     # name list of IO filler cell (string, optional)
-from <coord>         # staring offset from edge for adding fillers
                      # (float, optional)
-ioRow <rowName>      # name of IO row to be processed (string, optional)
-logic                # delete NON-physical IO filler (bool, optional)
-prefix <string>      # prefix for new filler instances (string, optional)
-to <coord>           # ending offset from edge for adding fillers
                      # (float, optional)